---
import CtaIcon from "../icons/ctaIcon.astro";
---

<section class="bg-fondo py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
      Ayuda al desarrollo de tu hijo
      <span class="block text-primary mt-2 text-5xl"
        >con apoyo especializado</span
      >
    </h2>

    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      En Nedeal creamos planes personalizados para el neurodesarrollo, lenguaje
      y aprendizaje infantil.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="/contacto"
        class="cursor-pointer transition-all bg-primary text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-3xl
        border-quaternary border-b-[4px] hover:brightness-110 hover:-translate-y-[1px]
        hover:border-b-[6px] active:border-b-[2px] active:brightness-90 active:translate-y-[2px]
        inline-flex justify-center gap-2 text-2xl"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="size-6"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          fill="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            d="M2 3a1 1 0 011-1h2.153a1 1 0 01.986.836l.74 4.435a1 1 0 01-.54 1.06l-1.548.773a11.037 11.037 0 006.105 6.105l.774-1.548a1 1 0 011.059-.54l4.435.74a1 1 0 01.836.986V17a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2C7.82 18 2 12.18 2 5V3z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        Agenda tu consulta
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-gray-500">
      MÃ¡s de 100 familias han confiado en nuestro equipo multidisciplinario
    </p>
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <CtaIcon class="size-48 lg:size-64 items-center" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
